quran[25]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,43,"Ojú wọn yóò wálẹ̀. Ìyẹpẹrẹ máa bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀. Wọ́n kúkú ti pè wọ́n síbi ìforíkanlẹ̀ nígbà tí wọ́n ní àlàáfíà (wọn kò sì kírun)."
  68,44,"Nítorí náà, fi Èmi àti ẹni tó ń pe ọ̀rọ̀ yìí ní irọ́ sílẹ̀. A óò máa dẹ wọ́n lẹ́kẹ láti jẹ wọ́n níyà ní àyè tí wọn kò mọ̀."
  68,45,"Mò ń lọ́ra fún wọn ni. Dájúdájú ète Mi lágbára.{1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:15.]
  69,40,"Dájúdájú al-Ƙur’ān ni ọ̀rọ̀ (tí A fi rán) Òjíṣẹ́, alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé.{1}.",1:[Āyah yìí jọ āyah 19 nínú sūrah at-Takwīr ní ìsọ, àmọ “Òjíṣẹ́” tí wọ́n gbàlérò nínú āyah ti sūrah al-Hāƙƙọh ni Òjíṣẹ́ abara, ìyẹn Ànábì wa Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -, Òjíṣẹ́ mọlāika ni wọ́n sì gbàlérò nínú āyah ti sūrah at-Takwīr. Sàkánì ti ìkọ̀ọ̀kan ti jẹyọ l’ó ṣàfi hàn èyí bẹ́ẹ̀.]
  69,41,"Kì í ṣe ọ̀rọ̀ eléwì. Ohun tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ kéré púpọ̀."
  69,42,"Kì í sì ṣe ọ̀rọ̀ adábigba. Díẹ̀ lẹ̀ ń lò nínú ìrántí."
  70,34,"àti àwọn tó ń ṣọ́ àwọn ìrun wọn."
  70,35,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé nínú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra."
  70,36,"Kí ló mú àwọn tí kò gbàgbọ́ tí ara wọn kò balẹ̀ níwájú rẹ,"
  72,28,"nítorí kí Ó lè ṣàfi hàn pé wọ́n ti jẹ́ àwọn iṣẹ́ Olúwa wọn dé ògòńgó. Àti pé Allāhu fi ìmọ̀ rọkiri ká ohun tí ń bẹ lọ́dọ̀ wọn. Ó sì ṣọ́ òǹkà gbogbo n̄ǹkan."
  74,19,"Wọ́n sì ṣẹ́bi lé e nípa bí ó ṣe pinnu."
  74,20,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Wọ́n tún ṣẹ́bi lé e nípa bí ó ṣe pinnu."
  74,21,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó wò sùn."
  75,16,"Má ṣe gbé ahọ́n rẹ sí ìmísí láti kánjú ké e."
  75,17,"Dájúdájú Àwa l’A máa ṣe àkójọ rẹ̀ (sínú ọkàn rẹ) àti kíké rẹ̀."
  75,18,"Nígbà tí A bá ń ké e (fún ọ), kí o sì máa tẹ̀lé kíké rẹ̀."
  76,10,"Dájúdájú àwa ń páyà ọjọ́ kan tí (ẹ̀dá yóò) fajú ro kókó ní ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wa.”"
  76,11,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu yóò ṣọ́ wọn níbi aburú ọjọ́ yẹn. Ó sì máa fún wọn ni ìtutù ojú àti ìdùnnú."
  76,12,"Ó sì máa san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra àti aṣọ àlàárì nítorí pé wọ́n ṣe sùúrù."
  77,7,"Dájúdájú ohun tí A ṣe ní àdéhùn fún yín kúkú máa ṣẹlẹ̀."
  77,8,"Nítorí náà, nígbà tí wọ́n bá pa (ìmọ́lẹ̀) ìràwọ̀ rẹ́,"
  77,9,"àti nígbà tí wọ́n bá ṣí sánmọ̀ sílẹ̀ gbagada,"
  78,4,"Rárá! Wọ́n ń bọ̀ wá mọ̀."
  78,5,"Lẹ́yìn náà, rárá sẹ́, wọ́n ń bọ̀ wá mọ̀."
  78,6,"Ǹjẹ́ Àwa kò ṣe ilẹ̀ ní ìtẹ́ bí,"